g.text: The algorithm is X16S (shuﬄe) on ﬁrst mention, then X16S after.
The organization is one word, ﬁrst letter capitalized: Pigeoncoin
Each project is lowercase: pigeonbrand, pigeonsite, pigeonpool
Assets will be hosted on Github whenever possible. Use individual projects.
All text is Helvetivca Neue 55 Roman. Monospace is Menlo Regular.
